OPTIVISION TECHN said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 28.79% to NT$84,482,000 from NT$118,642,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             84,482          118,642    
YOY%             -28.79%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            276,679          300,167    
YOY%              -7.82% 
=================================================================
 